tip_battle.title: Ixion (Savage)
tip_battle.message:
• ・Uses strong lightning attacks.
  • ・Casts Dispel and attacks that weaken resistance to lightning.
  • ・When defending, Defense and Resistance are raised and dealing damage becomes more difficult.
  • ・When evading, Evasion is raised and landing physical attacks becomes more difficult.
